trans-unit.source: This interface declares the methods required to support the `$expand` query option for an [!INCLUDE[ssAstoria](~/add/includes/ssastoria-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Dette grensesnittet deklarerer metoder for å støtte av `$expand` spørring alternativ for en [!INCLUDE[ssAstoria](~/add/includes/ssastoria-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Applies expansions to the specified queryable parameter.
trans-unit.target: Gjelder utvidelsene for den angitte queryable parameteren.

trans-unit.source: The ApplyExpansions method may modify the `expandPaths` to indicate which expansions are included.
trans-unit.target: Metoden ApplyExpansions kan endre den `expandPaths` til å angi hvilken utvidelsene er inkludert.

trans-unit.source: The returned <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> may implement the <xref:System.Data.Services.IExpandedResult> interface to provide enumerable objects for the expansions; otherwise, the expanded information is expected to be found directly in the enumerated objects.
trans-unit.target: Det returnerte <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>kan implementere den <xref:System.Data.Services.IExpandedResult>grensesnitt for å gi et tallsett objekter i utvidelsene; ellers utvidede informasjonen er forventet å finner direkte i nummererte objektene.</xref:System.Data.Services.IExpandedResult> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.Data.Services.ExpandSegmentCollection"></xref> paths to expand.
trans-unit.target: En samling av <xref href="System.Data.Services.ExpandSegmentCollection"> </xref> baner skal utvides.

trans-unit.source: An object of the same type as the supplied queryable object that includes the specified expandPaths.
trans-unit.target: En objekt av den samme typen som den angitte queryable objekt som inneholder den angitte expandPaths .
